{"about_the_game":"<strong><i>Knocking hats off &quot;Employee&quot;'s head</i></strong> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/803640/extras/hithat.gif?t=1690301400\" /><br><strong><i>Tossing props to distract employee, they'll go to investigate</i></strong> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/803640/extras/distract.gif?t=1690301400\" /><br><strong><i>You might consider using Magunet against more distant employee</i></strong> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/803640/extras/MagHit.gif?t=1690301400\" /><br><br><strong><i>Standing in the 2.25m\u00b2 place, Taking over all the stages</i></strong> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/803640/extras/2.25mxm300_2.png?t=1690301400\" /><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Defeat all enemies to proceed to the next room.<br></li><li>The enemies' only weak point is their hats. Throw objects at their hats to defeat them.<br></li><li>Challenge more than 60+ puzzles in the lowpoly world. More and more puzzles will be released afterwards.<br></li><li>Using various abilities such as magnetic, time, space, and various physical mechanisms to defeat all enemies.<br></li><li>Unique music and sound effects in harmony with the colorful visuals, all of them are inspired by plenty of YouTube music and meme culture.<br></li><li>No dizzy \u2014 only locomotion VR\u2014 in fact player will not leave the 2.25m\u00b2 area under feet.</li></ul></strong><br><br>Phantom Matrix is a theatrical, physics-based, stealth puzzle action game in Virtual Reality. You are a game developer whose game has been robbed, your mission is to seek the truth after all mankind has been possessed. Armed with your wits and the &quot;game&quot; power, it\u2019s time to save your game and friends.<br><br>7 Chapters, 7 Boss Leve